---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import { SOCIAL_LINKS, AUTHOR_NAME } from '../consts';
---
<BaseLayout
  title="About"
  description={`About ${AUTHOR_NAME} — Technical Director with 20+ years in game development and agentic AI.`}
>
  <div class="prose prose-invert prose-a:text-sky-400">
    <h1>About</h1>
    <p>
      Director of Engineering and Technical Director with 20+ years building
      games — from AAA multiplayer titles to 80+ mobile releases — and lately
      focused on bringing agentic AI into how engineering teams actually work.
    </p>
    <h2>Background</h2>
    <p>
      I’ve spent over two decades in software and game development, most of it
      leading technical teams and shipping at scale. I’m currently Technical
      Director at The Multiplayer Group, leading engineering teams building AAA
      multiplayer titles and engine tools in Unreal Engine 4/5 and advanced
      C++, with scalable backend architectures across Kubernetes, Docker, and
      the major cloud platforms.
    </p>
    <p>
      Before MPG, I was Technical Director at Activision Blizzard King, where I
      directed a team of 35+ engineers within a 120-person studio, shipped two
      mobile titles, and supported six live games serving millions of daily
      players. Earlier I led the engineering of the first metaverse game engine
      at Decentraland, was Principal Engineer and C++ lead across multiple game
      teams at King, and co-founded the mobile studio Unkasoft as CTO, where we
      released 80+ titles worldwide on our own C++ engine frameworks.
    </p>
    <p>
      My core has always been engine-level C++ — optimization, gameplay
      systems, and architecture — but what I care about now is the next shift:
      how agentic AI and tools like Claude Code change the day-to-day shape of
      building software. I write here about that, mostly through the lens of
      game development. I also teach agentic AI to development teams.
    </p>
    <h2>Expertise</h2>
    <ul>
      <li>Technical &amp; engineering leadership — directing teams of 35+, aligning technical execution with product vision</li>
      <li>AAA &amp; mobile game development — Unreal Engine 4/5, advanced C++, engine-level and gameplay systems</li>
      <li>Large-scale multiplayer &amp; backend architecture — Orleans, Pragma, Kubernetes, Docker, AWS/GCP/Azure</li>
      <li>Agentic AI for software teams — implementation strategy, tooling, and instruction</li>
      <li>Performance &amp; delivery — optimization, CI/CD automation, Agile at scale</li>
    </ul>
    <h2>Elsewhere</h2>
    <ul>
      <li><a href={SOCIAL_LINKS.github} rel="me noopener">GitHub</a></li>
      <li><a href={SOCIAL_LINKS.linkedin} rel="me noopener">LinkedIn</a></li>
      <li><a href={SOCIAL_LINKS.youtube} rel="me noopener">YouTube</a></li>
    </ul>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>